{"tid":504880,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救] 貴婦keep住有皮膚病","createTime":"2017-12-20T13:47:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-22T06:28:52.000Z","uid":81653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"84fbcb0d37c805d737f0bdca39be7ccb6633d675","tid":504880,"uid":81653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T13:47:12.000Z","msg":"2個月前隻貴婦開始成日R痕<br />\n仔細一睇個身好多甩皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇完醫生食完藥好返 無耐發現到佢jj發炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nJ頭紅晒又有晶體<br />\n睇完醫生食完藥好返 無耐發現佢眼角紅晒甩皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇完醫生食完藥好返 無耐發現佢jj又紅晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢段期間長期帶頭套唔俾佢lam都不斷翻發<br />\n平時靜係食狗糧同俾小小生果(橙, 梨)佢食<br />\n係咪佢抵抗力唔夠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n關唔關食開既狗糧唔好？(呢隻食左2年）<br />\n希望各位幫幫我 幫幫小狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a1b111650ef550ba60314c195300bfb3abe4681","tid":504880,"uid":29487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T14:03:09.000Z","msg":"屋企有無成日用漂白水/同類野拖地清潔，又無過乾淨水？"},{"pid":"4c7c45094a66cd6b5310de08c60c60044893ba31","tid":504880,"uid":37909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T14:07:17.000Z","msg":"我隻貴婦又係好鍾意R痕<br />\n睇醫生 醫生話係皮膚敏感<br />\n係因為抵抗力太強<br />\n咩都抵抗搞到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"481a9be7f8f1d482c2da5eee085c3b08370ff70f","tid":504880,"uid":37909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T14:08:42.000Z","msg":"仲有 醫生話狗狗食魚油丸對皮膚好的<br />\n可能你可以買啲魚油丸比佢食"},{"pid":"f66b47c57f92e4384f5320c5a4bbf575c23de37e","tid":504880,"uid":35943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T14:49:06.000Z","msg":"買狗正傻鳩"},{"pid":"c4aa534b782b754fcb64bb3f120aeb6f2461a866","tid":504880,"uid":145779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi